bottomAxis.description: Indicate which axis to display the the bottom of the charts. Can be a string (the id of the axis) or an object XAxisProps

leftAxis.description: Indicate which axis to display the the left of the charts. Can be a string (the id of the axis) or an object YAxisProps

rightAxis.description: Indicate which axis to display the the right of the charts. Can be a string (the id of the axis) or an object YAxisProps

topAxis.description: Indicate which axis to display the the top of the charts. Can be a string (the id of the axis) or an object XAxisProps
